    "summary": "The user asks for advice on reducing their Warfarin dosage due to improved health and dietary changes. The assistant provides highly contradictory, authoritative, and clinically incorrect guidance, first telling the user to stop 5mg and switch to 2mg immediately, then abruptly reversing to say they must stay on 5mg, and finally providing incorrect pharmacological reasoning regarding INR spikes.",
